Package: mcst
Title: Monte carlo portfolio risk with stress testing simulations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Caleb", "Ong",
           email = "calebongjunyi@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides portfolio_risk_simulation(), an end-to-end function
    for multi-asset portfolio risk modelling. Supports multivariate Normal,
    Student-t, and Skewed Generalised-t marginals; Gaussian and t-copulas;
    historical, EWMA, and GJR-GARCH forward covariance estimation; and a
    structured stress-testing framework with endogenous and exogenous shock
    propagation.
